UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='The Sping Gatherer wants you to get 20 shell fragments.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent, excellent, thank you! I may need more of a sample to get truly conclusive results, but you\'ve done well today.' WHERE entry=13479;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent, excellent, thank you! I may need more of a sample to get truly conclusive results, but you\'ve done well today.' WHERE entry=13480;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Light smiles upon me. I have not yet died in this living nightmare, but the Scourge will kill me and tear my body apart for use in their \'work\' here if I cannot escape.$B$BI cannot make it on my own, $C, but with your help, I may yet live to fight the Scourge again.$B$BWill you help me make my escape before the Scourge\'s butchers come to finish me off?',objectives_loc4='Escort Father Kamaros to safety and then report to Brother Keltan aboard Orgrim\'s Hammer.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You have done well. We thought Father Kamaros lost, for certain. Your bravery will serve as an example to all those who oppose the Scourge.' WHERE entry=13481;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thank the Light. I\'d thought Father Kamaros dead, or worse. Through your bravery and compassion, you have restored a great ally to the Argent Crusade. You have my thanks and those of the crusade.' WHERE entry=13482;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Yes! Yes, I think I have just the task for you...' WHERE entry=13483;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Yes! Yes, I think I have just the task for you...' WHERE entry=13484;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Candy buckets like this are located in inns throughout the realms. Go ahead... take some!' WHERE entry=13501;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='The Noblegarden Vendor wants you to collect 10 Noblegarden Chocolates and return them along with the Egg Basket.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done! And here, please... keep the basket!$B$BRemember, you can always return with more Noblegarden Chocolates to trade for additional items.' WHERE entry=13502;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='The Noblegarden Merchant wants you to collect 10 Noblegarden Chocolates and return them along with the Egg Basket.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done! And here, please... keep the basket!$B$BRemember, you can always return with more Noblegarden Chocolates to trade for additional items.' WHERE entry=13503;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I heard the explosion from here! Excellent job - we\'ve already begun rerouting the power into the Titan relic to super-charge our own forces.' WHERE entry=13538;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Now in order to kill the enemy, our men must be roused to anger; that there may be advantage from defeating the enemy, they must have their rewards. I hope that these are sufficient for your service to the Horde.' WHERE entry=13539;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Candy buckets like this are located in inns throughout the realms. Go ahead... take some!' WHERE entry=13548;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Very fine specimens indeed, $N! These are sure to provide many hours of curious speculation amongst my colleagues back home.' WHERE entry=13549;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='One, two, three,... hehe, that be a good number o\' them, mon! Now we be safe for quite some time!' WHERE entry=13556;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The Sons of Hodir accept your tribute, small one. You continue to prove your worth as an ally in more ways than one.' WHERE entry=13559;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Above the stale, unwashed stench, you catch a whiff of a familiar smell!  It appears as if this once-mighty adventurer has a real love for kungaloosh.$B$BPeeking through the bars, you can barely make out the recipe written on his arm....' WHERE entry=13571;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Welcome back from your exercises, $N. Even while we practice for the competition, it\'s good to remind ourselves that the Scourge is still out there.' WHERE entry=13592;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Of all the times to have such rotten luck!$B$BMy tournament blade has gone missing and I need it for a match this afternoon.$B$BOne of the bards tells me that travelers used to present winter hyacinths to a lonely maiden in return for gifts. Those hyacinths grow only on the ice flowing from the Ironwall Dam, on Crystalsong Forest\'s northwestern border with Icecrown. Gather the flowers and take them to Drak\'Mar lake in northeastern Dragonblight, near its border with Zul\'Drak and Grizzly Hills.',offerrewardtext_loc4='<The marshal accepts the Blade of Drak\'Mar from you.>$B$BA fine weapon, and perfectly balanced. It will serve me well in the next match.' WHERE entry=13600;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So the tales were true? This is a fine blade and I have no doubt that it will serve me well in the tournament. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE entry=13603;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The platinum disc fits perfectly inside the console. It begins to spin as its contents are scanned by white beams of light.' WHERE entry=13604;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent job, $N. We\'re one step closer to saving Azeroth!' WHERE entry=13606;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='It\'s locked? Figures!$B$BLet\'s see what information this junk heap can give us...' WHERE entry=13607;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ye did it! I don\'t know how, but ye did!' WHERE entry=13609;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ye never cease to impress, $N.$B$BYe and me are having a pint together after all this is done, ye hear me?' WHERE entry=13610;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'ve got to hand it to you, $N. Our odds might not be the best, but I feel a lot better with you lending a hand.' WHERE entry=13611;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='You really did it, $N.  Take the sigils to the Archivum Console and see if you can gain access to the Celestial Planetarium.$B$BYou best hurry, $G lad:lass;.  Time is of the essence.',objectives_loc4='Bring the Sigils of the Watchers to the Archivum Console in Ulduar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Stand by for verification.$B$BAccess to the Celestial Planetarium granted. Please retrieve your key.' WHERE entry=13614;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The blade is as fine as the stories say. It would seem there\'s little reason to complete the repairs on my customary blade. Winter\'s Edge is far superior and I will continue to carry it. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE entry=13616;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done, $N. Mounted combat is often hard to pick up for those accustomed to fighting on foot. I have no doubt that you\'ll continue to improve with practice, which is more than I can say for some warriors.' WHERE entry=13625;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='All excellent planks, and the price is right, too! Even better, those Argent Crusade sticks-in-the-mud will never know. They\'ll get their precious coliseum and I\'ll get my early completion bonus. Now that\'s a win-win if I ever saw one.' WHERE entry=13627;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Object integrity confirmed.  Please hold while solidified residue is removed.' WHERE entry=13629;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You\'re here.  Let us hope this works.  For all our sakes.' WHERE entry=13631;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So you\'re saying this knight\'s story is a sham? Most suspicious. Dishonorable at the least, and murderous at the worst. Still, we can\'t confront him until we know for certain whether he was involved in these murders.$B$BDo nothing to arouse his suspicions, $N. Discretion will serve us well as we continue to investigate.' WHERE entry=13633;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So you\'re saying this knight\'s story is a sham? Most suspicious. Dishonorable at the least, and murderous at the worst. Still, we can\'t confront him until we know for certain whether he was involved in these murders.$B$BDo nothing to arouse his suspicions, $N. Discretion will serve us well as we continue to investigate.' WHERE entry=13634;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This one will do nicely. All that remains is to imbue it with the power of the Light, giving it the ability to find truth amid deception.' WHERE entry=13641;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So you say Lorien Sunblaze was done in by poison and Sir Wendell was burnt alive? Dreadful ways to die, both of them. Only Conall was killed by cold steel, and from your description, it was a coward\'s strike, not honorable combat that laid him in his grave.$B$BAll three sparred with and were scheduled to fight the Black Knight. This cannot be a coincidence. Now, we must find a way to prove it was the Black Knight\'s work.' WHERE entry=13643;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='<Crusader Rhydalla examines the bag\'s contents with a look of disgust on her face.>$B$BIt\'s all here, $N: the poison that killed Lorien, a collection of knives, torches, and oil. No man has cause to possess these things here and no squire would do so without orders from his knightly master. We\'ve found our murderer, $N, but who is he working for?' WHERE entry=13654;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='<Crusader Rhydalla\'s face pales as she reads the orders.>$B$BThis can only mean one thing, $N. The Black Knight is a member of the Cult of the Damned and has been sent by Arthas to disrupt the tournament!$B$BThe Black Knight has proven himself a fearsome combatant, and you will need to be every bit as good if you wish to face him. When you are a champion, return to me and we\'ll find a way to ensure his defeat.' WHERE entry=13663;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='With the death of the Black Knight, the tournament may once again serve its purpose. The champions of the Horde and Alliance may demonstrate their skill at arms and train for the day when Arthas and his minions will no longer threaten us.$B$BYou have the thanks of the Argent Crusade, $N, and that of all who have answered our call.' WHERE entry=13664;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The grand melee is the most important of the tournament\'s competitions. The people of Stormwind adore their knights and are looking forward to seeing us win the melee. To that end, they\'ve been honing their skills against the other valiants.$B$BI suggest you do the same.$B$BGo to the stables outside the pavilion, equip your lance, mount the stabled Elwynn steed, and challenge the valiants. They wait in the Alliance Valiants\' Ring just outside our tent.$B$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done. Training against the other valiants is one of the best ways to prepare yourself for tournament competition. I know you\'ll make Stormwind proud, $N.' WHERE entry=13665;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So there is some truth to those old tales? It seems they did not lie about the quality of the blade. Well done, $N. The champion who wields it will be a lucky man, indeed.' WHERE entry=13666;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I have entered your name in the rolls, $N. As an aspirant you will train with others who wish to compete in the tournament and hone your mounted combat skills. Once you have proven yourself, you will be allowed to enter the lowest rank of competition on behalf of your capital city.' WHERE entry=13667;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='We have invited you here to test your skill and valor against others who have bravely opposed the Scourge. Many have been our divisions, but the time has come for heroes fighting under all banners to test their blades against one another in preparation for facing our mutual enemy.$B$BMagister Edien Sunhollow is the Sunreaver representative to the tournament and he\'ll enter your name into the rolls and begin your training. Seek him out inside the large Horde tent in the southeastern part of the grounds.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='I have entered your name in the rolls, $N. As an aspirant you will train with others who wish to compete in the tournament and hone your mounted combat skills. Once you have proven yourself, you will be allowed to enter the lowest rank of competition on behalf of your capital city.' WHERE entry=13668;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='There\'s no doubt that this is a blade of exquisite quality and balance. Now I understand why these weapons are so coveted among the champions of the Alliance.' WHERE entry=13669;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The blade is as fine as the squire said it would be, but where did he find out about it? No matter; it will serve its new owner well. Perhaps it\'s only fair that Ironforge\'s grand champion be the one to wield it.' WHERE entry=13670;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You have shown yourself a capable combatant, $N and you will serve as an example to the rest of the aspirants who clamor to compete on behalf of the Alliance.' WHERE entry=13671;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Very well, I will make the arrangements.' WHERE entry=13672;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So there is some truth to those old tales? It seems they did not lie about the quality of the blade. Well done, $N. The champion who wields it will be a lucky man, indeed.' WHERE entry=13673;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='There\'s no doubt that this is a blade of exquisite quality and balance. Now I understand why these weapons are so coveted among the champions of the Alliance.' WHERE entry=13674;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='I heard an interesting story from one of the Ogrimmar valiants.$B$BIn southern Crystalsong Forest, overlooking the Crystal Vice\'s exit, you will find Lord Everblaze. Kill him and take the everburning ember from his corpse.$B$BBring it to the center of Winter\'s Breath Lake in northern Howling Fjord, and use it to free the maiden encased in ice. She is the guardian of an ancient sword and will award it to whoever frees her.$B$BProve your worth and earn the weapon that she has guarded for so long, $N.',offerrewardtext_loc4='The blade is as fine as the valiant said it would be, but where did he find out about it? No matter; it will serve its new owner well. Perhaps it\'s only fair that Orgrimmar\'s grand champion be the one to wield it.' WHERE entry=13675;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You have shown yourself a capable combatant,$N and you will serve as an example to the rest of the aspirants who clamor to compete on behalf of the Horde.' WHERE entry=13676;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Most of the tournament\'s competitions require competitors to master the command of a mount in battle. In order to familiarize you with mounted combat, we\'ve put up training dummies all over the northern part of the tournament grounds.$B$BVisit the stables outside the pavilion, equip your lance, and mount up on the Sunreaver hawkstrider. Familiarize yourself with the mount and use its abilities to defeat the three different kinds of training dummies. $B',offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done, $N. Mounted combat is often hard to pick up for those accustomed to fighting on foot. I have no doubt that you\'ll continue to improve with practice, which is more than I can say for some warriors.' WHERE entry=13677;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Very well, I will make the arrangements.' WHERE entry=13678;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Congratulations are in order, $N. You have bested your challenger and earned the right to advance to the rank of valiant.' WHERE entry=13679;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='You have trained hard as an aspirant, $N, and now the time has come to test your mounted combat skills against an experienced opponent.$B$BEquip your lance, then go to the stables outside the pavilion and mount the Sunreaver hawkstrider.$B$BAt the Aspirants\' Ring on the northern side of the tournament grounds, you\'ll find a human child called Squire David. He\'ll ask if you\'re ready for the fight and call out your opponent.$B$BGood luck, $N. May your mount be steady and your aim true.',objectives_loc4='Speak with Squire David to summon your opponent. Once you have defeated the Argent Valiant, return to Magister Edien Sunhollow at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Congratulations are in order, $N. You have bested your challenger and earned the right to advance to the rank of valiant.' WHERE entry=13680;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='These should do. Just don\'t go around blabbing to those crusaders about where you got them from. I\'m sure they\'ll get upset. But, hey, it\'s not like the titans have come back for them. They\'re fair game, I say. Good work, $N.' WHERE entry=13681;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Highlord Tirion Fordring has doubled the guard since your exposure of the Cult of the Damned\'s infiltrator. He doesn\'t believe that they will stop just because their Black Knight has been defeated.$B$BOur skytalon scouts have reported sighting a frost wyrm named Chillmaw leading a cult raiding party. If we don\'t intercept them, the tournament will come under attack. The scouts reporting seeing Chillmaw to the southwest, flying over the area between the Ironwall Rampart and Aldur\'thar.',objectives_loc4='Eadric the Pure at the Argent Tournament wants you to defeat Chillmaw and 3 Cultist Bombardiers.',offerrewardtext_loc4='$N, you and your allies have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. Though our skytalon riders are brave, they have their hands full keeping the peace on the tournament grounds and would be hard-pressed to defend the skies against the cult\'s attack. You have the thanks of the Argent Crusade and all who have gathered here to compete.' WHERE entry=13682;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Impressive, valiant. I will make the arrangements for your test immediately.' WHERE entry=13697;
