UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So the tales were true? This is a fine blade and I have no doubt that it will serve me well in the tournament. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE entry=13741;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Of all the times to have such rotten luck!$B$BMy tournament blade has gone missing and I need it for a match this afternoon.$B$BOne of the bards tells me that travelers used to present winter hyacinths to a lonely maiden in return for gifts. Those hyacinths grow only on the ice flowing from the Ironwall Dam, on Crystalsong Forest\'s northwestern border with Icecrown. Gather the flowers and take them to Drak\'Mar lake in northeastern Dragonblight, near its border with Zul\'Drak and Grizzly Hills.',offerrewardtext_loc4='<The grand champion accepts the Blade of Drak\'Mar from you.>$B$BA fine weapon, and perfectly balanced. It will serve me well in the next match.' WHERE entry=13742;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The blade is as fine as the stories say. It would seem there\'s little reason to complete the repairs on my customary blade. Winter\'s Edge is far superior and I will continue to carry it. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE entry=13743;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Welcome back from your exercises, $N. Even while we practice for the competition, it\'s good to remind ourselves that the Scourge is still out there.' WHERE entry=13744;
