UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The grand melee is the most important of the tournament\'s competitions. Victory will not be easy, but I am confident that we will win. You must practice with your mount until the two of you work as one.$B$BIt will help prepare you for the rigors of tournament combat.$B$BGo to the stables outside the pavilion, equip your lance, mount the stabled Silvermoon hawkstrider, and challenge the valiants. They wait in the Horde Valiants\' Ring just outside our tent.$B$B',objectives_loc4='Bring 3 Marks of the Valiant to Aneera Thuron at the Argent Tournament Grounds.$B$BIf you lose your lance, you can get another from any of the Lance Racks near the stables or in the Silver Covenant Pavilion.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Training against the other valiants will sharpen your claws and hone your battle insticts. When the competition begins, you will be ready.' WHERE entry=13787;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Argent Crusade has doubled the guard since your exposure of the Cult of the Damned\'s infiltrator. They know the cultists won\'t stop until they\'ve destroyed this area and thwarted the tournament.$B$BThe Argent Crusade\'s scouts have reported sighting a frost wyrm named Chillmaw leading a cult raiding party.$B$BYou must intercept and destroy them before they attack. The scouts reporting seeing Chillmaw to the southwest, flying over the area between the Ironwall Rampart and Aldur\'thar.',objectives_loc4='Crok Scourgebane at the Argent Tournament wants you to defeat Chillmaw and 3 Cultist Bombardiers.',offerrewardtext_loc4='$N, you have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. The Argent Crusade and all who gather here are in our debt and we\'ll make certain they remember it. For all their bluster about providing protection, the peacekeepers and skytalons spend more time breaking up drunken brawls than keeping us safe from the Scourge.$B$BIt\'s no matter. We always protect our own.' WHERE entry=13788;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You are a true champion, $N, both inside the ring and on the field. We must all be vigilant against the Scourge and you are a great example to our brethren and your own people.' WHERE entry=13789;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Bring 4 Marks of the Champion to Luuri at the Argent Tournament Grounds.$B$BIf you lose your lance, you can get another from any of the Lance Racks near the stables or in the Silver Covenant Pavilion.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done. Training against the other valiants is one of the best ways to prepare yourself for tournament competition. I know you\'ll make the Alliance proud, $N.' WHERE entry=13790;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You have done well in demonstrating our commitment to fighting the Scourge, no matter where we are or what we are doing.' WHERE entry=13791;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You handle your mount well, $N. In time, your competitors will learn to fear you.' WHERE entry=13793;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='I have asked my brothers of the Argent Crusade to work closely with those who rise to the rank of champion. Eadric the Pure, our brotherhood\'s grand champion, helps oversee training exercises for champions from all cities and helps them make their final preparations for tournament competition.$B$BPlease go and introduce yourself to him. I know he\'ll be eager to meet you and work with you on your way to competing against Azeroth\'s greatest champions.',objectives_loc4='Speak with Eadric the Pure at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',offerrewardtext_loc4='It\'s good to finally meet you, champion. The highlord has asked me to help coordinate the efforts of all champions to train together and bolster the defenses of the tournament grounds.' WHERE entry=13794;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Highlord Tirion Fordring has doubled the guard since your exposure of the Cult of the Damned\'s infiltrator. He doesn\'t believe that they will stop just because their Black Knight has been defeated.$B$BOur skytalon scouts have reported sighting a frost wyrm named Chillmaw leading a cult raiding party. If we don\'t intercept them, the tournament will come under attack. The scouts reporting seeing Chillmaw to the southwest, flying over the area between the Ironwall Rampart and Aldur\'thar.',objectives_loc4='Eadric the Pure at the Argent Tournament wants you to defeat Chillmaw and 3 Cultist Bombardiers.',offerrewardtext_loc4='$N, you and your allies have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. Though our skytalon riders are brave, they have their hands full keeping the peace on the tournament grounds and would be hard-pressed to defend the skies against the cult\'s attack. You have the thanks of the Argent Crusade and all who have gathered here to compete.' WHERE entry=13809;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You are a true champion, $N, both inside the ring and on the field. We must all be vigilant against the Scourge and you are a great example to our brethren and your own people.' WHERE entry=13810;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done. Training against the other valiants is one of the best ways to prepare yourself for tournament competition. I know you\'ll make the Horde proud, $N.' WHERE entry=13811;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Argent Crusade has doubled the guard since your exposure of the Cult of the Damned\'s infiltrator. They know the cultists won\'t stop until they\'ve destroyed this area and thwarted the tournament.$B$BThe Argent Crusade\'s scouts have reported sighting a frost wyrm named Chillmaw leading a cult raiding party.$B$BYou must intercept and destroy them before they attack. The scouts reporting seeing Chillmaw to the southwest, flying over the area between the Ironwall Rampart and Aldur\'thar.',objectives_loc4='Crok Scourgebane at the Argent Tournament wants you to defeat Chillmaw and 3 Cultist Bombardiers.',offerrewardtext_loc4='$N, you have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. The Argent Crusade and all who gather here are in our debt and we\'ll make certain they remember it. For all their bluster about providing protection, the peacekeepers and skytalons spend more time breaking up drunken brawls than keeping us safe from the Scourge.$B$BIt\'s no matter. We always protect our own.' WHERE entry=13812;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You have done well in demonstrating our commitment to fighting the Scourge, no matter where we are or what we are doing.' WHERE entry=13813;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='As a champion, you have mastered the art of mounted combat, overcoming challengers of all levels. You must make certain that you can defeat anyone you face when the tournament begins.$B$BYou should continue honing your own skills and learning more about the weaknesses of your opponents. Champions representing all cities practice in the Ring of Champions near the stables. Go to the stables, equip your lance, pick any mount you can ride, then face the champions in practice bouts.',objectives_loc4='Bring 4 Marks of the Champion to Illyrie Nightfall at the Argent Tournament Grounds.$B$BIf you lose your lance, you can get another from any of the Lance Racks near the stables or in the Sunreaver Pavilion.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You handle your mount well, $N. In time, your competitors will learn to fear you.' WHERE entry=13814;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='It\'s locked?  Figures!$B$BI\'ll let Brann know... maybe he can uncover something in the Archivum.' WHERE entry=13816;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The platinum disc fits perfectly inside the console. It begins to spin as its contents are scanned by white beams of light.' WHERE entry=13817;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You\'re here.  Let us hope this works.  For all our sakes.' WHERE entry=13819;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So the justicar sent you to see us? Good, good...$B$BWe could always use more help with the, uh, "requisition" of materials.' WHERE entry=13820;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent job, $N. We\'re one step closer to saving Azeroth!' WHERE entry=13821;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ye did it! I don\'t know how, but ye did!' WHERE entry=13822;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ye never cease to impress, $N.$B$BYe and me are having a pint together after all this is done, ye hear me?' WHERE entry=13823;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'ve got to hand it to you, $N. Our odds might not be the best, but I feel a lot better with you lending a hand.' WHERE entry=13824;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Keep the words of the master in mind as you practice with the training dummies.' WHERE entry=13828;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Keep the words of the master in mind as you practice with the training dummies.' WHERE entry=13829;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So eating it makes you invisible... what a strange defense this clever fish has developed.$B$BI\'d like to digest this for a bit. Pun not intended, $N. Really. Why don\'t you come see me tomorrow?' WHERE entry=13830;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Well now, that looks like it could be valuable. Difficult to know until it\'s cleaned up and appraised, but I\'m still willing to make the trade if you are.' WHERE entry=13832;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You are a brave one, $N. I hope you didn\'t lose any extremities making your fishing spot. If you\'ve still got the fishing bug, come back tomorrow and we\'ll talk some more.' WHERE entry=13833;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='My, my, my! You\'ve caught yourself some Terrorfish. Why, that reminds me of the time...$B$B<Marcia regales you with stories of adventure and fishing for as long as you\'re willing to listen.>' WHERE entry=13834;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Commit Valis\'s lesson to memory, $N. It will mean the difference between winning and losing your mounted combat matches.' WHERE entry=13835;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Oh, hello there $N. Marcia said you\'d be coming by with that poor man\'s missing arm.$B$BShe also gave me this bag to give you as a reward. It smells horrible, and I\'m anxious to make the trade if you don\'t mind.' WHERE entry=13836;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='With a teacher like Rugan, you\'ll be an expert at mounted combat in no time.' WHERE entry=13837;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Commit Valis\'s lesson to memory, $N. It will mean the difference between winning and losing your mounted combat matches.' WHERE entry=13838;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='With experience and practice, you will become deadly with the charge.' WHERE entry=13839;
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc4='The Scrapbot Construction Kit',details_loc4='Searching the databanks of the prototype console reveals schematics for a scrapbot construction kit. With your engineering expertise, you could learn this schematic and produce scrapbot construction kits of your own.' WHERE entry=13843;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Bring the Seal Vial of Poison to Alchemist Cinesra in the Dalaran Sewers.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You are brave to have carried this. If even one drop were to touch your skin, you\'d have died an agonizing death.$B$BAllow me to pay you for it... I can always use venom of exceptional potency.' WHERE entry=13845;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thank you. I just know the crusade will put it to good use!' WHERE entry=13846;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders what they already knew -- that our warriors are more than just parade ground decorations.' WHERE entry=13847;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='You want to ride a Venomhide? Then I\'ve got bad news for you.$B$BThe Venomhide Ravasaurs, they\'re all poison: Poison blood, poison spit, poison skin. You climb on one, you fall off dead in a few hours.$B$BYou\'d have to build up a resistance to their toxins before I sold you one, and that takes a long, LONG time... you\'d need to be splashed with poisonous blood while fighting one numerous times. If you\'re really interested, the venomhides prefer the northern area of of the Marshlands, northwest of here.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You did it? You actually did it?!$B$BHo ho! Stubborn as my wife, you are.' WHERE entry=13850;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that we are worthy allies.' WHERE entry=13851;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the that we are a match for the Argent Crusade\'s own.' WHERE entry=13852;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders what they already knew -- that our warriors are more than just parade ground decorations.' WHERE entry=13854;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that they can rely on us in the battle against the Lich King.' WHERE entry=13855;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders what they already knew -- that our warriors are the best in Azeroth.' WHERE entry=13856;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that we are fearless in the face of the Lich King\'s minions.' WHERE entry=13857;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Anka Clawhoof at the Argent Tournament Grounds wants you to kill 15 Boneguard Footmen, 10 Boneguard Scouts, 3 Boneguard Lieutenants.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that we are steadfast allies in the battle against the Lich King.' WHERE entry=13858;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that we are ready to face any enemy.' WHERE entry=13859;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Handler Dretch at the Argent Tournament Grounds wants you to kill 15 Boneguard Footmen, 10 Boneguard Scouts, 3 Boneguard Lieutenants.',offerrewardtext_loc4='The Argent Crusade has seen our resolve and they know that our warriors will see this through to the end.' WHERE entry=13860;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The Argent Crusade is heartened to have $Cs like you fighting alongside us in the battle against the Lich King.' WHERE entry=13861;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The Argent Crusade is heartened to have $Cs like you fighting alongside us in the battle against the Lich King.' WHERE entry=13862;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Everywhere we have met the Scourge, we have made them fear us, and this campaign is no different.' WHERE entry=13863;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Everywhere we have fought the Scourge, we have taught them to fear us and this campaign will be no different.' WHERE entry=13864;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The venomhide hatchling looks at you expectantly, then begins to scrawl a pictogram into the dirt.$B$BThe hatchling\'s drawings seem to resemble various types of large insects, perhaps the gorishi silithids. The hatchling finishes his picture, then gestures at it with one short arm, snaps its jaws, and licks its lips.$B$BIt must want you to go to the Slithering Scar, in center of the southern part of Un\'Goro Crater, and gather silithid meat. When you have the meat, feed it to your hungry hatchling.',objectives_loc4='Your Venomhide Hatchling wants you to feed it 10 Silithid Meat.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Your venomhide hatchling flashes you a toothy smile and then settles in for a nap.' WHERE entry=13903;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your hatchling licks its lips after devouring the meal of silithid eggs. For a moment, you think it seems disappointed that feeding time has come to an end.' WHERE entry=13904;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='It looks like both of you have managed to do some growing without killing one another.$B$BThere, everything\'s finished. I\'ve trained your venomhide ravasaur to respond when you blow this whistle.$B$BFew have the dedication to hand-feed and raise a venomhide, but they\'re well worth the effort.' WHERE entry=13906;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your hatchling licks its lips after devouring the meal of silithid eggs. For a moment, you think it seems disappointed that feeding time has come to an end.' WHERE entry=13916;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The venomhide hatchling looks at you expectantly, then begins to scrawl a pictogram into the dirt.$B$BThe hatchling\'s drawings seem to resemble various types of large insects, perhaps the gorishi silithids. The hatchling finishes his picture, then gestures at it with one short arm, snaps its jaws, and licks its lips.$B$BIt must want you to go to the Slithering Scar, in center of the southern part of Un\'Goro Crater, and gather silithid meat. When you have the meat, feed it to your hungry hatchling.',objectives_loc4='Your Venomhide Hatchling wants you to feed it 10 Silithid Meat.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Your venomhide hatchling flashes you a toothy smile and then settles in for a nap.' WHERE entry=13917;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You take us away from puppy-men hatchlings? Good. We like you already. Mean puppy-men hatchlings took all our favorite toys away.' WHERE entry=13926;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You take Kekek hunting? Good to get away from mean old orphan lady who doesn\'t let Kekek hunt.' WHERE entry=13927;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='We never knew trees got that big! Nope. Maybe Great Ones had special plan for it?' WHERE entry=13929;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is Kekek\'s kind of city. Bear-men fight for home just like Frenzyheart do. Orphan lady tell Kekek not to fight with other pups, but Kekek fight anyway.' WHERE entry=13930;
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc4='Another Year, Another Souvenir.',details_loc4='Brewfest isn\'t just about racing rams, it\'s also about drinking!  When you have a moment, take this voucher to Belbi Quikswitch.  She\'s near the back of the Brewfest camp.  If you can\'t see her, don\'t worry, she\'ll be sure to see you.$B$BIn any case, take this voucher to her to get your free Brewfest stein.  She\'ll also be more than happy to handle any and all other Brewfest transactions.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Aww, it\'s just a stein voucher... Maybe you\'re just playing hard to get.  So here\'s this year\'s stein for you.$B$BBut I suspect I\'ll be seeing a lot more of you.  After all, if you want any Brewfest tokens redeemed, I\'m your girl...$B$BOr maybe I\'m his girl...  $B$BOooohhh... or his...' WHERE entry=13932;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='We very glad you brought us here, $N. We always worried what would happen to us when the orphan matron found us in Sholazar.' WHERE entry=13933;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='See? Kekek never get tired of saying, "Kekek tell you so."$B$BMaybe now you believe other things Kekek tell you, like how sky is green.' WHERE entry=13934;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='That was fun! We like toy store. Maybe orphan matron take us sometimes. We ask. Maybe you tell her too?' WHERE entry=13937;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='That was fun! We go again sometime? We can\'t wait to see our new friend again!' WHERE entry=13950;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Kekek like new Snowfall friends, maybe come back and go hunting together sometime. Maybe we go tip over walrus-men when they sleeping.' WHERE entry=13951;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=13952;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Do you think she ever saw an oracle before? We might be the first one ever to meet her! We thinks she liked us, but we\'re not sure. She doesn\'t talk a lot. Nope. But that was fun!' WHERE entry=13954;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Kekek always liked dragons. Always wanted to be one, but orphan-lady said no. But she did say maybe you take Kekek to meet dragon queen.$B$BKekek think orphan-lady have good idea for once. You take Kekek to Wyrmrest Temple in the middle of Dragonblight? Fly all the way to top to meet dragon queen. She must be really big, to be queen of all dragons. Kekek can\'t wait to see!',objectives_loc4='Take your orphan, Kekek, to visit Alexstrasza the Life-Binder at the top of Wyrmrest Temple. Make sure to call for him if he is not present when you get there.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Queen not what Kekek expected, but Kekek understand why. Queen\'s visitors get crushed if she was always big dragon! Still want to see someday.' WHERE entry=13955;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='We got to meet a Great One! Too bad it was during his nap time, but we understand. We like naps, too! Maybe we learn naps from Great Ones like we learn about shrines and shinies!$B$BCan we come back and visit the Great One again when not sleeping?' WHERE entry=13956;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You help Kekek learn him a book? Then, Kekek hunt with Hemet Nesingwary!' WHERE entry=13957;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='We had the best time with you, $N. We wish you could be our $G daddy : mama; now, but you have to take us back to Orphan Matron Aria in Dalaran.$B$BMaybe you could come visit us again sometime? We loved meeting Winterfin hatchlings and getting to see the dragon queen. No one will believe us when we say we met a Great One!$B$BWe going to miss you, $N. We promise to write letter sometime, oki?',objectives_loc4='Return your ward to the Dalaran orphanage by handing in the Oracle Orphan Whistle to Orphan Matron Aria in Dalaran.',offerrewardtext_loc4='It sounds like little Roo had a great time this week. I know he was getting awfully lonely in the orphanage and was eager to make some new friends. Thank you so much for agreeing to look after him.' WHERE entry=13959;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Know what? You not so bad after all, $N. You take Kekek a lot of fun places. Kekek meet a lot of new friends and do things no other pup get to do.$B$BYou, and Hemet Nesingwary, and Snowfall Glade pups all new best friends. Maybe sometime you bring Kekek that green hills book? Kekek promise to write sometimes, too, tell you how things go. Maybe even be nice to big-tongue kids sometimes.$B$BKekek gotta go back to orphan-lady Aria now, back in purple human city.',objectives_loc4='Return your ward to the Dalaran orphanage by handing in the Wolvar Orphan Whistle to Orphan Matron Aria in Dalaran.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Thank you for agreeing to care for Kekek this week. I know he can be a handful, but I think that with more individual attention and a few more friends, he\'ll do a lot better. No doubt he\'s going to be telling stories of his adventures with you for weeks.' WHERE entry=13960;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Oh, my shield! I won\'t be using it anytime soon, but thank you. I hate that I\'m sitting here useless when I could be helping on the front, but fighting with my arm like this won\'t help anyone.$B$BTake care out there, won\'t you?' WHERE entry=13986;
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc4='The Black Knight\'s Curse',objectives_loc4='Crusader Rhydalla at the Argent Tournament Grounds wants you to investigate the Black Knight\'s Grave.',offerrewardtext_loc4='<Crusader Rhydalla frowns.>$B$BDo you think they\'ve been planning this? I suppose it doesn\'t matter, but I don\'t like the implication that we\'ve been playing into their hands. Whatever is going on, we have to stop it.' WHERE entry=14016;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='If you\'d like to learn to cook Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, I can help. If you\'re not already a cook, all you have to do is train and you\'ll be cooking in no time!' WHERE entry=14022;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent. This is just what we needed. It\'s going to be a chore keeping all the tables stocked with fresh food, but it\'s well worth it.' WHERE entry=14023;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The pumpkin pie\'s been a big hit up here. I\'ve never seen a dwarf get so excited about anything made from a vegetable.' WHERE entry=14024;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Finally, the cranberry chutney I was promised. You wouldn\'t believe how fast the celebrants go through the stuff here.' WHERE entry=14028;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thanks for bringing everything. I was starting to get worried.$B$BWhile you\'re here, you should try your hand at making some candied sweet potatoes.' WHERE entry=14030;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Kill 8 Kobold Vermin, then return to Marshal McBride.' WHERE entry=14032;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='While you\'re here, you might want to stock up on Teldrassil sweet potatoes. They\'re used to make the most delicious candied sweet potatoes you\'ve ever tasted.$B$BIf you don\'t believe me, look up the recipe in your bountiful cookbook and give it a try. And if there are any extras, you might want to share them with Gregory Tabor at the feasting area just outside Stormwind. They\'re one of his favorites, but to hear him tell it, everything\'s his favorite!',objectives_loc4='Make 5 servings of Candied Sweet Potatoes and bring them to Gregory Tabor just outside the gates of Stormwind.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, candied sweet potatoes! My favorite! Did Isaac tell you?' WHERE entry=14033;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Every Pilgrim\'s Bounty feast requires a magnificent centerpiece, and I\'m not talking about a decorative horn of plenty, either. No, the focus of the meal is a magnificent roast turkey.$B$BThere\'s a good recipe for it in your bountiful cookbook. Why not hunt some wild turkeys and prepare a few? The turkeys wander all over Elwynn Forest, so you shouldn\'t have a problem finding one.$B$BOnce you\'re done roasting them, will you bring them to Isaac Allerton near the gates of Darnassus?',objectives_loc4='Make 5 Slow-Roasted Turkeys and bring them to Isaac Allerton near the gates of Darnassus.',offerrewardtext_loc4='These are beautiful and just in time to feed hungry feasters. Thank you, $N. You\'ve truly mastered all the courses of a traditional Pilgrim\'s Bounty meal.' WHERE entry=14035;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='If you\'d like to learn to cook Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, I can help. If you\'re not already a cook, all you have to do is train and you\'ll be cooking in no time.' WHERE entry=14036;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='It\'s a chore keeping all these tables stocked. If you stop and think about it, it\'s strange going to so much trouble when we needn\'t eat anymore.$B$B<William shrugs.>$B$BTradition is tradition.' WHERE entry=14037;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='That spice bread stuffing you made is a hit, but no Pilgrim\'s Bounty feast is complete without a slice of pumpkin pie. It\'s another traditional local dish, since it uses ripe Tirisfal pumpkins that only grow around here.$B$BIf you don\'t know how to make pumpkin pie already, there\'s a recipe in your bountiful cookbook.$B$BWould you mind cooking up a few slices and bringing them to Francis Eaton outside Orgrimmar? He\'s bound to be running low by now.',objectives_loc4='Make 5 slices of Pumpkin Pie and bring them to Francis Eaton at the feasting area right outside Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='The pie always goes first. I think people must be skipping the meal and going directly for the dessert. Have you given it a try yet?' WHERE entry=14040;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Have you tried the cranberry chutney yet? It\'s made with fresh tangy Southfury cranberries. Just pick some up from the Pilgrim\'s Bounty vendor if you want to try your hand at making chutney.$B$BThe recipe should be in your bountiful cookbook.$B$BIf you\'ve got some extra time on your hands, would you mind making some of the chutney and bringing it to Dokin Farplain at the base of the elevator on the western side of Thunder Bluff.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more cranberry chutney! You wouldn\'t believe how fast the celebrants go through it.' WHERE entry=14041;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='While you\'re here, you might want to stock up on Mulgore sweet potatoes. They\'re used to make delicious candied sweet potatoes, my favorite part of the Pilgrim\'s Bounty meal.$B$BIf you don\'t believe me, look up the recipe in your bountiful cookbook and give it a try. If you\'re headed back to Orgrimmar, bring them to Francis Eaton at the feasting area just outside the city. I\'ve been trying to keep him supplied, but everything goes so fast over there.',objectives_loc4='Make 5 servings of Candied Sweet Potatoes and bring them to Francis Eaton just outside of Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So Dokin drafted you to help with the candied sweet potatoes?$B$B<Francis smiles.>$B$BIt\'s the only way he can keep up. Thanks for bringing these.' WHERE entry=14043;
UPDATE locales_quest SET ObjectiveText1_loc4='Prepare Candied Sweet Potato' WHERE entry=14043;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thanks for bringing everything. Some of the tables were starting to look a little bereft of serving dishes.' WHERE entry=14044;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Every Pilgrim\'s Bounty feast requires a centerpiece, and for us, that\'s a slow-roasted wild turkey. I can\'t think of anything better to bring the meal together.$B$BThere\'s a good recipe for it in your bountiful cookbook. Why not hunt some wild turkeys and prepare a few? The turkeys wander all over Tirisfal Glades, so you shouldn\'t have a problem finding any.$B$BOnce you\'re done roasting them, will you bring them to Francis Eaton outside Orgrimmar?',objectives_loc4='Make 5 Slow-Roasted Turkeys and bring them to Francis Eaton near the gates of Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='These look perfect. Thank you, $N. You\'ve truly mastered all the courses of a traditional Pilgrim\'s Bounty meal.' WHERE entry=14047;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='These are just what I need. Thanks, $N. You\'re a lifesaver.' WHERE entry=14048;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thank goodness! I wouldn\'t be able to serve the feast without spice bread stuffing.' WHERE entry=14051;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thanks. This looks great, and you\'re a fair bit faster than Jasper, but don\'t tell him I said so.' WHERE entry=14053;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='These are perfect. Isaac, and everyone else, will love them!' WHERE entry=14054;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='These are perfect. Thanks for helping me with this, $N. The meal will get served on time and Ellen will be happy.' WHERE entry=14055;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thanks, $N. Now, I can help the hostess out and still keep my word to Roberta.' WHERE entry=14058;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thanks for your help, and let me know if you ever get to the bottom of the case of the disappearing chutney.' WHERE entry=14059;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='These are great! Thank you for helping, $N.' WHERE entry=14060;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='These turkeys are exactly what I needed. Thanks for helping me out of a tough situation.' WHERE entry=14061;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Perfect timing! I wouldn\'t be able to serve the feast without spice bread stuffing.' WHERE entry=14062;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='What a feast, hmmm?$B$BI\'m so glad you could celebrate the spirit of Pilgrim\'s Bounty with us.' WHERE entry=14064;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='What a feast, hmmm?$B$BI\'m so glad you could celebrate the spirit of Pilgrim\'s Bounty with us.' WHERE entry=14065;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Argent Crusade dispatched a fast ship carrying tallstrider meat and other supplies for us here at the tournament grounds, but it never arrived. Scouts reported seeing it attacked by the kvaldir, fearsome vrykul raiders who roam the seas.$B$BThey\'ve slain the crew and taken the cargo to an island called Hrothgar\'s Landing. If you look to the north, you can see it shrouded in the mist. Would you help us in recovering the stolen supplies? Without those tallstrider legs, we\'ll soon be out of food.',offerrewardtext_loc4='These look a little worse for wear, but they\'re still edible. The crusaders will be glad to hear that we\'ve managed to recover some of the ship\'s cargo.' WHERE entry=14074;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done, $N. I\'ll take these to the Argent Crusade\'s keepers right away. They\'ll have no choice but to acknowledge that we\'re doing far more than the Sunreavers to keep the coliseum running smoothly.' WHERE entry=14076;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='<Narasi accepts the prayer book from you.>$B$BThank you. The book was a gift from Confessor Paletress herself. She would be honored to know that you have used it to bring tranquility to the slain.' WHERE entry=14077;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14079;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Your actions have shown that we stand as one with the Argent Crusade, while the Sunreavers are too busy preening to take up their blades.' WHERE entry=14080;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Perascamin.$B$BPerascamin can be found at Thuron\'s Livery, southeast of the Shepherd\'s Gate leaving Silvermoon City.',objectives_loc4='Return the pamphlet to Perascamin at Thuron\'s Livery in Silvermoon City.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14081;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Aalun.$B$BAalun can be found at the entrance to the Exodar on Azuremyst Isle.',objectives_loc4='Return this pamphlet to Aalun outside the Exodar on Azuremyst Isle.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14082;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Ultham Ironhorn.$B$BUltham can be found at the Amberstill Ranch in Dun Morogh, found along the road east out of Ironforge.',objectives_loc4='Return the pamphlet to Ultham Ironhorn at Amberstill Ranch in Dun Morogh.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14083;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Binjy Featherwhistle.$B$BBinjy can be found at Steelgrill\'s Depot, just northeast of Kharanos in Dun Morogh.',objectives_loc4='Return the pamphlet to Binjy Featherwhistle at Steelgrill\'s Depot in Dun Morogh.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14084;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Jartsam.$B$BJartsam can be found at the Cenarion Enclave in Darnassus.',objectives_loc4='Return the pamphlet to Jartsam at the Cenarion Enclave in Darnassus.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14085;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Kildar.$B$BKildar can be found in Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Honor.',objectives_loc4='Return the pamphlet to Kildar in Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Honor.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14086;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Kar Stormsinger.$B$BKar can be found in Mulgore\'s Bloodhoof Village.',objectives_loc4='Return the pamphlet to Kar Stormsinger at Bloodhoof Village in Mulgore.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14087;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Xar\'Ti.$B$BXar\'Ti can be found at Sen\'jin Village in southern Durotar.',objectives_loc4='Return the pamphlet to Xar\'Ti at Sen\'jin Village in southern Durotar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14088;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Velma Warnam.$B$BVelma can be found at Brill in Tirisfal Glades.',objectives_loc4='Return the pamphlet to Velma Warnam at Brill in Tirisfal Glades.',offerrewardtext_loc4='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE entry=14089;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Sunreavers the care of this creature. They\'re enough alike that they ought to be able to understand each other.' WHERE entry=14090;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Now that the coliseum is complete, the Argent Crusade has asked us to help look after the creatures that champions will be fighting.$B$BThe giant jormungar have perhaps the strangest diet; they grow strong by eating the eggs of their own kind and the best eggs come from deep jormungar.$B$BTake this drum to the Foot Steppes in central Storm Peaks and play them near the snow mounds you see there. The sound will rouse the deep jormungar. Kill them, collect their egg sacs, and return to the tournament grounds.',objectives_loc4='Acquire 4 Jormungar Egg Sacs and bring them to Tylos Dawnrunner at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'ll let the crusaders know that you\'ve just returned with a fresh load of food while the Silver Covenant was sitting on its heels.' WHERE entry=14092;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I knew that Kraken was not a match for the likes of you.  Without that Kraken disrupting those boats, those Kvaldir will have no choice but to retreat.  Great job, Champion!' WHERE entry=14095;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Thanks to you, Kul and the aspirants will live fight the Scourge again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. My only hope is that the crusaders can find a better outlet for his enthusiasm than allowing him to impart all of his bad habits to impressionable young aspirants.' WHERE entry=14096;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The kvaldir, seafaring vrykul who raid ships and coastal settlements, have overrun a tuskarr  island across the strait to the north. Their leader is a veteran raider, Drottinn Hrothgar, who seeks to control these seas.$B$BWith him in power, our shipments and troop transports will never be safe. We will be stranded here at the Lich King\'s mercy.$B$BTake this captured kvaldir war horn to the circle of tuskarr statues on the northeastern part of Hrothgar\'s Landing and use it to challenge the kvaldir leader.',offerrewardtext_loc4='The defeat of the drottinn will set the kvaldir to fighting amongst themselves, buying us time to use our advantage. The crusade and the tournament are in your debt, champion.' WHERE entry=14101;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You have bought us valuable time to move against the Kvaldir and free the seas of these pests. Once again, the Argent Crusade is in your debt.' WHERE entry=14102;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Ornolf the Scarred is a fearsome raider renowned among his Kvaldir brethren for raiding and capturing ships. From aboard Bor\'s Fury, he and his crew attack our ships and steal our goods.$B$BOrnolf and his men are among those who slaughtered the inhabitants of a tuskarr island to the north and renamed it Hrothgar\'s Landing. His ship sits at anchor at the eastern end of the island\'s harbor. Take this captured banner and display it on his ship to provoke him into facing you in battle.',objectives_loc4='High Crusader Adelard at the Argent Tournament Grounds wants you to kill Ornolf the Scarred.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ornolf\'s crew will want to avenge their leader, but without him, they will be easier to defeat. We must live to carry out our mission, to see Icecrown rid of the Scourge and other evils.' WHERE entry=14104;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You are truly an example to all who have gathered beneath our banner, $N. Together, we will show the Scourge that we will not be defeated.' WHERE entry=14105;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You have done our fallen brethren a great service and spared us the need to face them again on the field of battle. As our campaign against the Scourge progresses, I find myself thinking about my own fate.$B$BShould I fall, $N, I would want someone like you to do for me what you have done for the spirits of the fallen this day. I could not bear the thought of forcing my own brothers to slay me again and again.' WHERE entry=14107;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Crusader Silverdawn wants you to mount an Argent Hippogryph, throw 6 Flaming Spears at the North Sea Kraken and take out 3 Vrykul Deepcallers.$B$BYou can find the Argent Hippogryphs right outside the Argent Crusade tent at the Tournament Grounds.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Crusader, you may have bought those sailors just enough time to escape, Maybe next time, those Silver Covenant and Sunreavers will listen before running head first at the enemy.' WHERE entry=14108;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Sunreavers.' WHERE entry=14112;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Great job, Champion. The fight continues, but now the Kvaldir know that we do not tolerate such attacks.' WHERE entry=14136;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Giranan the Blooded at the Argent Tournament Grounds wants you to kill 10 Kvaldir.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Your actions have shown that we Sunreavers are far better allies to the Argent Crusade than the Silver Covenant and it is we who will be triumphant.' WHERE entry=14140;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Use the Weighted Net to capture 8 Snowblind Followers and bring them to Tylos Dawnrunner at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',offerrewardtext_loc4='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Silver Covenant the care of this creature. They\'re going to have to get their hands dirty when the battle for Icecrown Citadel starts and I have a feeling they\'ll prove fragile and fussy allies.' WHERE entry=14141;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Crusader Kul has gone and gotten himself into trouble again, only this time he\'s not alone. When he saw the cultists making camp at Deathspeaker\'s Watch, west of the tourney grounds, Kul gathered the aspirants for an attack.$B$BThey were easily captured, and now Kul languishes in a cage on the platform in the camp. I am sure that the cult will sacrifice the prisoners unless we can rescue them. Any of those cultists could carry keys to the black cages. Find the keys and free Kul and the captive aspirants.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='Kul will live to embarrass himself again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. With examples like him, it\'s no wonder most of the aspirants are taking up the habits of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE entry=14142;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Argent Crusade dispatched a fast ship carrying tallstrider meat and other supplies for us here at the tournament grounds, but it never arrived. Scouts reported seeing it attacked by the kvaldir, fearsome vrykul raiders who roam the seas.$B$BThey\'ve slain the crew and taken the cargo to an island called Hrothgar\'s Landing. If you look to the north, you can see it shrouded in the mist. Would you help us in recovering the stolen supplies? Without those tallstrider legs, we\'ll soon be out of food.',objectives_loc4='Recover 10 Stolen Tallstrider Legs for Girana the Blooded at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',offerrewardtext_loc4='These look a little worse for wear, but they\'re still edible. The crusaders will be glad to hear that we\'ve had some success. Maybe we can give the half-eaten ones to the Silver Covenant. That would make my day.' WHERE entry=14143;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='I\'ve been listening to Confessor Paletress speak, and I must tell you, her words have made me think. We fight beside the crusaders, but we can learn from them, too.$B$BOff the north coast is Hrothgar\'s Landing, where the seagoing Kvaldir have overrun an old tuskarr settlement and slain the villagers. Take this book and read the rites for the dead near the corpses of the villagers. It will allow their spirits to escape the mists engulfing the island and find peace.',objectives_loc4='Use the Confessor\'s Prayer Book to perform last rites for 8 Slain Tualiq Villagers and then return to Girana the Blooded at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',offerrewardtext_loc4='<Girana accepts the prayer book from you.>$B$BThank you. We don\'t always see eye-to-eye with the crusaders, but I\'ve learned a lot from Confessor Paletress in my time here.' WHERE entry=14144;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE entry=14145;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Very good, $N.$B$BNow, the trick is to align the facets just right...' WHERE entry=14151;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='It seems things are worse than we initially thought. You still made a valiant effort and saved many of The Wavecrest\'s crew\'s lives.' WHERE entry=14152;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is a fine list of deeds, $N!  You are to be rewarded handsomely for your accomplishments.' WHERE entry=14160;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The Horde will never be a match for our forces as long as we have people like you on our side, $N.' WHERE entry=14163;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Nothing will stand between us and total victory. For the Horde!' WHERE entry=14164;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14166;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Dwarf Spirit in Ironforge\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14167;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Gnome Spirit in Ironforge\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14168;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Draenei Spirit in The Exodar\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14169;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Night Elf Spirit in Darnassus\' graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14170;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Blood Elf Spirit in Silvermoon City\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14171;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14172;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14173;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Forsaken Spirit in Undercity\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14174;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Orc Spirit in Orgrimmar\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14175;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Tauren Spirit in Thunder Bluff\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14176;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Troll Spirit in Orgrimmar\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE entry=14177;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent news,$C! If our tactical deployments continue to be this successful, the Horde will be in full retreat before long.' WHERE entry=14178;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='We\'ve come one step closer to achieving total victory over the Horde. We cannot allow the enemy to obtain a foothold in this world or any other.' WHERE entry=14179;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE entry=14180;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE entry=14181;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='We will fight and crush the enemy wherever we find them.  Azeroth, Outland, the place makes no difference.$B$BWe cannot allow the Alliance to establish superiority in the Eye of the Storm.  Take the battle to them today... tomorrow it might be too late!',objectives_loc4='Win an Eye of the Storm battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran,  or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You bring honor to us all, $N. We must show the enemy that we will fight them wherever we find them.' WHERE entry=14182;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Alliance is an insidious enemy, $N.  They claim to defend the Ashenvale forests to justify their acts of aggression against our territories in the Barrens.$B$BToday we have an opportunity to drive the enemy from our lands once and for all.  Go to Warsong Gulch and take back what is rightfully ours!',objectives_loc4='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE entry=14183;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is quite a find, <name>. I can\'t have you selling this to anyone else, so I\'m willing to offer generously.' WHERE entry=14203;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The order has come down, $C. Sylvanas herself has requested that I send my most \'capable\' agents back to the Undercity for a highly sensitive tactical operation.$B$BUnfortunately, my most capable agents were killed over three years ago. In their stead I have a collection of brain dead riff-raff.$B$B<Nathanos stares coldly at you.>$B$BTravel to the Undercity at once and report to the Dark Lady. Do not embarrass me, $C!',objectives_loc4='Travel to the Undercity and speak with Lady Sylvanas Windrunner.',offerrewardtext_loc4='The Grand Crusader sits safely in the Scarlet Bastion while his forces pour into our lands, desecrate our structures and monuments and murder our people.$B$BThe time has come to deal with this pest. You will become the instrument of our reckoning.' WHERE entry=14349;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='We cannot attack the Scarlet Crusade\'s command directly; they are too well defended. But there\'s more than one way to skin a cat. They\'ll be nothing without their main force.$B$BThe Deathstalkers have been collecting data on the activity of the Crusade outside of Stratholme. Each day, a report is sent from their central command to Tyr\'s Hand. This report is the key, $R! Find the Crimson Courier and recover that report. Bring it to Nathanos.' WHERE entry=14350;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Because you fought with such valor and perseverance in the Battle of Hillsbrad, I have written this commendation, extolling your heroics in combat for the high command to recognize.$B$BTake this sealed commendation to Bragor Bloodfist in the Undercity.  Go with pride, $C.',objectives_loc4='Take Darthalia\'s Sealed Commendation to Bragor Bloodfist in the Undercity.' WHERE entry=14351;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Take the Small Scroll to Bragor Bloodfist in the Undercity.',offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'ve seen the insignia on this scroll before during my time in Northrend. You say this was on that crone who leads the pigs in Razorfen Kraul?$B$BI\'ll be damned if I\'m going to let the Scourge get a foothold here. The one who wrote this - this Malcin - is one of the Lich King\'s servants, obviously, and that makes him a target. Your target.$B$BThey\'re not going to take Kalimdor.' WHERE entry=14352;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Supposedly this Malcin is outside Razorfen Downs. There\'s no question - he has to die.$B$BMy contacts in Orgrimmar tell me their scouts have found signs of the Plague down there. The quilboar are showing signs of being plagued, too; they\'re much more powerful. Whatever the Scourge are doing down there needs to end. Now.$B$BFind this Malcin and kill him. Report back here when he\'s dead.',objectives_loc4='Bring Ambassador Malcin\'s Head to Bragor Bloodfist in the Undercity.' WHERE entry=14353;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'m sure Sylvanas will be glad to have that problem taken care of, $N. The task I gave you wasn\'t easy, but here you stand, victorious. That commands respect, and what you\'ve done won\'t be forgotten.' WHERE entry=14355;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Good, $C. You\'ve done well. I\'ll keep these safe from prying eyes; the last thing we need is a strong Shadow Council rising up again.$B$BCheck back with me in the future; there\'s always something that needs doing around here, apparently, and I might need another able body.' WHERE entry=14356;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Ah, the writings of Daros. He always was meticulous about tracking progress. His words may aid in explaining how far we\'ve come.$B$BYou have my thanks for bringing this to me, $R. Perhaps we will see more of each other once it is understood we mean no harm.' WHERE entry=14409;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Syndicate? I would never have suspected. It seems the lords of Alterac have fallen far in the years since their betrayal.$B$BHawkins will be pleased to learn of this, and as you were so instrumental in this discovery, it would be fitting if you were the one to deliver it to him.$B$BAh, and how could I forget?$B$BWelcome to the Deathstalkers.',objectives_loc4='Deliver Andron\'s Ledger to Aleric Hawkins in the Hall of the Dark Lady in the Undercity.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Hmm, this is interesting. The Deathstalkers have performed their duties admirably in ferreting this out.$B$BAs I\'m told, you deserve a reward for your part in these matters. Keep this up, $N; the Deathstalkers always have use of a good man.' WHERE entry=14418;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The letter of introduction should be enough to convince Andron that you are the messenger he\'s been waiting for. I\'ve met Andron before, he doesn\'t quite have the mental capacity to be that suspicious.$B$BOur leader suspects that Andron has been providing aid to some other group. He wishes to know what organization this is and requires proof of it.$B$BI want you to speak with Andron, and obtain this information. You\'ll find him at his shop near the Apothecarium.' WHERE entry=14419;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='If you wish to join the Deathstalkers, the Dark Lady\'s elite guard, you will have to prove your worth.$B$BI will not lie to you, $N, this task could mean your death.$B$BI have some things that need attending to. I require the personal effects of Astor Hadren, a messenger who travels between Silverpine and the Undercity. I will leave the method of procurement to your discretion.$B$BIt will be better for you if you know less of the nature of this business. Succeed and I shall tell you more.' WHERE entry=14420;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='For you to continue with the Rites of the Earthmother you must pass two more tests. It is time for you to broaden your experience, $N.$B$BTravel to Bloodhoof Village and seek out the Ahmo Thunderhorn. There you may continue your journey and earn the acceptance of the elders of Thunder Bluff.$B$BTake this totem to Ahmo. He will recognize my carvings and help you on your path.$B$BFollow the road out of Camp Narache and travel with haste. Do not stray or you will lose your way.',objectives_loc4='Take the Totem of Hawkwind to Ahmo Thunderhorn in Bloodhoof Village. Follow the road out of Camp Narache.' WHERE entry=14437;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Kill 10 Palemane Tanners, 8 Palemane Skinners, and 5 Palemane Poachers, then return to Ahmo Thunderhorn in Bloodhoof Village.' WHERE entry=14438;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='You will now be revered within our great city. Any $R worthy of completing the Rites of the Earthmother earns that honor.$B$BFor your final quest, seek out our young leader, Baine Bloodhoof, who dwells atop the highest mesa in Thunder Bluff.',objectives_loc4='Speak with Baine Bloodhoof in Thunder Bluff.' WHERE entry=14439;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Baine Bloodhoof in Thunder Bluff wants you to bring him the Horn of Arra\'chea.' WHERE entry=14440;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='They say that Garrosh Hellscream is one of the greatest heroes in the Horde! When I grow up, I want to be a hero of the Horde too!$B$BDo you know Garrosh, $N? Could you do me a favor, please? Could you get his autograph for me? I dunno how to ask him, and he probably wouldn\'t listen to someone like me... but you! You\'re an adventurer, like him! I bet he\'d give you his autograph easy!$B$BPlease?',objectives_loc4='Travel to Orgrimmar to see about getting Garrosh Hellscream\'s autograph for your ward.' WHERE entry=14441;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='<Caladis takes the hilt from you and slowly turns it over in his hands.>$B$BThis seems somehow familiar, as though I should know its origins. You say you recovered this in the citadel? Most intriguing.$B$BThere are few who possess the ability to make such a blade. Perhaps they can tell us something about your find.' WHERE entry=14443;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='We can\'t let that book remain in Sunreaver hands. If we hope to identify the sword and use it to our advantage, we have to find a way to capture the book Krasus lent them.' WHERE entry=14444;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='<Arcanist Tybalin examines the captured orders.>$B$BThe agent you intercepted was supposed to transport the Wyrmrest Tome to Icecrown, after meeting with one Magister Hathorel in Sunreaver\'s Sanctuary. We have to get that book, $N, and this is our chance. It\'s not going to be easy, though.' WHERE entry=14457;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='What we do here is none of your business...' WHERE entry=14488;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I knew Shandy would find a way to come through for us. Let me get this enchanted and ready for you to use. The sooner you get done with the tabard, the sooner we can get it back to Shandy and the better the chances that its owner will never have missed it.' WHERE entry=20438;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent work. Now that this is in our hands, we must get it to Caladis Brightspear as soon as possible. We can\'t risk the book falling back into Sunreaver hands.$B$BI\'ll ensure that Shandy Glossgleam gets his tabard back without incident, along with a healthy reward for his help.' WHERE entry=20439;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Alliance is an insidious enemy, $N.  They claim to defend the Ashenvale forests to justify their acts of aggression against our territories in the Barrens.$B$BToday we have an opportunity to drive the enemy from our lands once and for all.  Go to Warsong Gulch and take back what is rightfully ours!',objectives_loc4='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE entry=24216;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Alliance is an insidious enemy, $N.  They claim to defend the Ashenvale forests to justify their acts of aggression against our territories in the Barrens.$B$BToday we have an opportunity to drive the enemy from our lands once and for all.  Go to Warsong Gulch and take back what is rightfully ours!',objectives_loc4='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE entry=24217;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE entry=24218;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE entry=24219;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent news, $C! If our tactical deployments continue to be this successful, the Horde will be in full retreat before long.' WHERE entry=24220;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE entry=24221;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent news, $C! If our tactical deployments continue to be this successful, the Horde will be in full retreat before long.' WHERE entry=24223;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE entry=24224;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Alliance is an insidious enemy, $N.  They claim to defend the Ashenvale forests to justify their acts of aggression against our territories in the Barrens.$B$BToday we have an opportunity to drive the enemy from our lands once and for all.  Go to Warsong Gulch and take back what is rightfully ours!',objectives_loc4='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE entry=24225;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE entry=24226;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='We\'ve recently come extremely close to driving the Stormpike invaders from Alterac Valley.  As a result we\'re redirecting all our reinforcements to aid the Frostwolf Clan.$B$BA decisive victory there would free up the resources we need to crush the Alliance scum on all the other battlefronts.$B$BGo, $N.  Earn great honor by heeding the call of the brave Frostwolf warriors.',objectives_loc4='Win an Alterac Valley battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran or Shattrath.',offerrewardtext_loc4='There is no greater honor than driving invaders from Horde territories. We salute your great courage in aiding our forces today!' WHERE entry=24426;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Win an Alterac Valley battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran or Shattrath.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='Just what I wanted to hear!  A victory in Alterac Valley - even a temporary one - is crucial to our overall strategy against the Horde.' WHERE entry=24427;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='What? How did you get this? Isn\'t she... Never mind the details, I suppose. You\'ll be wanting one of these baubles as recompense, no doubt.' WHERE entry=24428;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='You have accomplished the truly impossible. The brood mother of the Black Dragonflight lies dead at your feet. Seize her head and deliver it to Neeru Fireblade.',objectives_loc4='Take the Head of Onyxia to Neeru Fireblade in the Cleft of Shadow.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You\'ve brought me the head of someone who is... No, best not to think about it too hard. You\'ll be wanting recompense for your heroic deeds, no doubt.' WHERE entry=24429;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is quite a find, $N. I can\'t have you selling this to anyone else, so I\'m willing to offer generously.' WHERE entry=24431;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='<Mariel accepts the orders and the captured seeing crystal and examines both.>$B$BGood work, $N, and quick thinking. I\'m sure the theft of this trinket won\'t slow them down for long, but I think you\'ve bought us time to warn the leaders of the Horde and Alliance about the impending attacks.' WHERE entry=24442;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='<Caladis accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BI knew the symbols on the blade were familiar. The weapon was most certainly forged by the dragons and gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE entry=24454;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar, although Blood-Queen Lana\'thel proclaimed we could not! The blade must still be tempered, but she and her master will not stand in our way!' WHERE entry=24461;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I... I don\'t understand. Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade to its original condition. What has happened here?' WHERE entry=24476;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I had not thought it possible for evil to take hold in such a sword, but I suppose it was naive of me. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BUther\'s advice is wise, $N, and I would urge you to heed it quickly.' WHERE entry=24480;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='They\'ve put our captured soldiers to work in the quarry! Kill their captors and set them free, hero, and do it quickly. We will need their aid when we confront Scourgelord Tyrannus.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE entry=24498;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='I cannot thank you enough for coming. We\'re severely undermanned to be risking a venture into the citadel, but opportunities like this are too rare to pass up.$B$BI\'m awaiting the arrival of champions from the coliseum, but if your reputation holds true, you should be more than equipped to fight through the forge yourself. Clear the way to the far side and secure the passage to the Pit of Saron. We will need to hold it to move our men further into the citadel.$B$BPlease hurry, $N. We\'re counting on you.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Just in time! Thank you, $N.$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... or maybe, just maybe, his redemption.' WHERE entry=24499;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Uther knew a great deal about how Arthas might be defeated. It\'s hard to believe that there is much hope of defeating Arthas upon the steps of his own throne. And who will take up the crown of Lich King if it comes to that?$B$BMany questions remain, but the answers that you\'ve uncovered may be critical to ensuring Arthas\' defeat. You need to find Jaina and escape the Lich King while there\'s still time.',objectives_loc4='Find Lady Jaina Proudmoore and escape the Halls of Reflection',offerrewardtext_loc4='<Jaina is still catching her breath.>$B$BI can barely believe we\'re still alive. It was foolish of me to follow him. I\'ve made that mistake too many times.  And you... it was reckless of you to come after me instead of escaping with the information! But... well... thank you. You truly are a hero.$B$BWith Uther\'s guidance, we may stand a chance at defeating Arthas. All the lives lost today were not in vain.' WHERE entry=24500;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Good. $N, I know of you. You\'ll be perfect for these tasks.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE entry=24506;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='They\'ve put our captured soldiers to work in the quarry. Kill their captors and set them free, $C, and do it quickly. We will need their aid when we confront Scourgelord Tyrannus.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE entry=24507;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='$N! I\'m so glad you\'ve come.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE entry=24510;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='I\'m glad we have someone capable to aid us in this. Delving into the citadel with so few is risky at best, but opportunities like this are too rare to pass up.$B$BI\'m awaiting the arrival of champions from the coliseum, but if your reputation holds true, you should be more than equipped to fight through the forge yourself. Clear the way to the far side and secure the passage to the Pit of Saron. We will need to hold it to move our men further into the Citadel.$B$BBe quick about it, $N. Time is short.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Well timed, $C!$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... and a route to vengeance long overdue.' WHERE entry=24511;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Admit you to the Sunwell? That\'s impossible! The Sunwell is the most sacred and important site of our people. We have only recently reclaimed it with the help of the Shattered Sun Offensive. It is not a place for tourists or travelers.' WHERE entry=24522;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I confess that I did not expect Thalorien\'s spirit to recognize you as the heir to Quel\'Delar, but I defer to his judgment. You may enter the Sunwell, but I remind you that you are a guest in the most our most sacred of precincts, and you should act accordingly.' WHERE entry=24535;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Get a load of these guys, would ya? Steamwheedle\'s been handling the business of holidays for years, and all of a sudden, these guys bust into the market. They\'re not Steamwheedle; the cartel hired me to get to the bottom of this. Something stinks here and it ain\'t just perfume.$B$BTake this device I brought and go analyze the perfume clouds around the guards. I want to know what they\'re putting in that stuff. Things ain\'t natural.' WHERE entry=24536;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='I knew they were up to no good! There\'s some sort of mind-affecting chemical in here, but I can\'t get a handle on it with such a small sample. I need the real stuff.$B$BDon\'t just go over there and buy it! I don\'t want you giving these scumbags one copper. Nah, you gotta get it from the source, discreet-like.$B$BI\'ll disguise you as a package runner. I saw a stockpile guarded by their goons outside the gates. Go run by, and DON\'T stop, or they\'ll make you! They\'ll toss you a crate. Bring it back here.' WHERE entry=24541;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='A deep sense of dread washes over you as the flame devours the items.' WHERE entry=24545;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Shadow\'s Edge is among the greatest weapons a $C could hope to obtain.$B$BIs your lust for power sated, $R?$B$B<You feel Mograine\'s penetrating gaze.>$B$BI thought not. A final warning then...$B$BYou now embark on the most treacherous leg of your quest. Bridle your aspirations, for if your aims are impure then your life, your very soul, is forfeit.$B$BThe weapon you hold is but an empty husk, a mere shadow of what it may become. Only by devouring a thousand souls shall its true potential be unlocked.',objectives_loc4='Highlord Darion Mograine wants you to use Shadow\'s Edge to slay 1000 of the Lich King\'s minions in Icecrown Citadel. Souls can be obtained in 10 or 25 person difficulty.' WHERE entry=24547;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE entry=24553;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This battered old sword hilt has seen better days. Before the hilt was snapped from the blade, it must\'ve been a magnificent example of the blacksmith\'s art.$B$BThe graceful symbols and exotic gemstones decorating the hilt suggest that the weapon may have belonged to a powerful person. Surely, the Sunreavers would be interested in hearing about the recovery of such an artifact. Seek out their representatives at Quel\'Delar\'s Rest, to the south of the Argent Tournament Grounds.',objectives_loc4='Bring the Battered Hilt to Myralion Sunblaze at Quel\'Delar\'s Rest, south of the Argent Tournament Grounds.',offerrewardtext_loc4='<Myralion takes the hilt from you and scrutinizes the artifact.>$B$BThis came from the citadel? What was it doing there? This blade is certainly not of Scourge manufacture.$B$BWeapons of this quality can only be crafted by a few of Azeroth\'s creatures. We will have to consult them and see if they can help us identify it.' WHERE entry=24554;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='There\'s no mistaking it - this hilt comes from a powerful, ancient weapon, but which one? I do not recognize these particular markings, but we haven\'t hit a dead end yet.$B$BKorialstrasz, better known as Krasus, has long been a friend to the quel\'dorei and the Kirin Tor. With his vast knowledge and resources, he\'s certain to know something. Travel to the top of Wyrmrest Temple and seek his counsel, then report to Magister Hathorel inside Sunreaver\'s Sanctuary in Dalaran.',offerrewardtext_loc4='We must recover that book from the Silver Covenant. Without that book from Krasus, we stand little chance of solving the mystery of the sword in Icecrown or unlocking its power.' WHERE entry=24555;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Getting you inside the Silver Enclave will be tougher than it appears. Only those who possess Silver Covenant tabards are permitted entry to sanctuary. If we can get our hands on one, a simple enchantment will do the rest of the work.$B$BOn the balcony above Threads of Fate, you\'ll find Shandy Glossgleam. I\'ve helped him a few times in the past, so he owes me a favor. He handles laundry for a wide variety of people in the city. Maybe he can find a way to \'lend\' you a tabard for a while.',offerrewardtext_loc4='I knew Shandy would find a way to make it work. Let me get this enchanted and ready for you to use. With any luck, the tabard\'s owner won\'t even know it\'s missing and Shandy will cover the rest of our tracks.' WHERE entry=24556;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Obtain 5 Infused Saronite Bars and the Forgemaster\'s Hammer, then combine them with the Remnants of Quel\'Delar to create the Reforged Quel\'Delar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar in defiance of that Blood-Queen Lana\'thel\'s pronouncement! Now, the blade must be tempered before we can show her the folly of her words.' WHERE entry=24559;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='At last, the pieces of Quel\'Delar are rejoined and the blade is whole, but it cannot see battle until you have tempered it. That jagged saronite edge is brittle and will shatter the moment it strikes anything.$B$BDeep in Icecrown Citadel\'s Forge of Souls is a place where the blade can safely be tempered. Take Quel\'Delar with you to the abode of the Devourer of Souls and look for the crucible. Plunge the blade into the crucible to temper it and bring it back to me. I\'ll be waiting in The Frozen Halls.',objectives_loc4='Temper the Re-forged Quel\'Delar in the Crucible of Souls.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade. Why hasn\'t it worked?' WHERE entry=24560;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='How can evil take root in such a sword? I would not have thought it possible if the evidence wasn\'t here before my eyes. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BI believe Uther is right. You must heed his advice quickly, $N.' WHERE entry=24561;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Take Quel\'Delar to the Sunwell as quickly as possible, $N. Trust in Uther\'s words when he says that you will not always be able to control the blade while it is subject to the evil of the Lich King\'s influence. You must travel to the Isle of Quel\'Danas, and there, seek entry to the Sunwell itself, where you can cleanse the sword.$B$BThe guardians will try to stop you from entering the Sunwell Plateau, but make yourself known to Halduron Brightwing, who will be inspecting the guards there.',offerrewardtext_loc4='I hope you understand that I can\'t just admit you to the Sunwell, $N. This is the most sacred place known to the sin\'dorei and we have only recently regained control over it.$B$BYou would raise the hopes of our people with tales of Quel\'Delar? Without proof of the truth of your claims, I see no reason to take you at your word.' WHERE entry=24562;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='You are the one working with Myralion Sunblaze, arent you? I know of a way we can test the sword.$B$BIf you know the blade\'s history, you recall that it was borne by Thalorien Dawnseeker in defense of the Sunwell against the Scourge. He fell in what is now the Dead Scar, buying time for his men to make their own preparations. You will find his remains near the southern end of the Dead Scar on this isle. Visit them, and if his spirit gives you its blessing, I will allow you to enter the Sunwell.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You truly do carry Quel\'Delar. This is a great day for all of Quel\'Thalas and the sin\'dorei. You have my leave to enter the Sunwell and finish the sword\'s restoration. Keep your head high, $N. The children of Silvermoon have dreamt of this day for years.' WHERE entry=24563;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Sunwell and the end of Quel\'Delar\'s exile await, $N.$B$BYou will find Lor\'themar Theron, the regent of Quel\'Thalas, and Grand Magister Rommath standing within. Be wary and do not allow them to entrap you in their political scheming.$B$BInstead, remain focused on your task here. Speak to a Warden of the Sunwell when you are ready to enter the Sunwell. Immerse the reformed Quel\'Delar in the Sunwell to complete the restoration. Afterward, show the blade to Myralion Sunblaze at Quel\'Delar\'s Rest.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE entry=24564;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='<Roka listens with disgust as you tell her why you\'re trying to track down Snivel.>$B$BYou mean I\'ve been under the spell of an alchemist all this time? I can\'t believe I fell for that fraud! If I ever get my hands on that conniving little goblin, I\'ll tear him apart!$B$BIf he\'s finished his errands, he\'s on his way down to the zeppelin tower east of Orgrimmar\'s gates! Whatever you do, $N, you can\'t let him board that zeppelin and get away with all this!$B$BHurry to the zeppelin tower before you miss him!',objectives_loc4='Go to the zeppelin tower outside Orgrimmar and question Snivel Rustrocket about the supplies. Return with any evidence he gives you.' WHERE entry=24576;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='With Sartharion slain, surely Deathwing and Sinestra\'s plans are now stalled.' WHERE entry=24579;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Word of your success precedes you, $C. Anub\'Rekhan is no more. You did him a great service, $N.' WHERE entry=24580;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='That\'s one less thorn in our side. With Noth destroyed, Scourge research into refining the means of creating the undead will grind to a halt.' WHERE entry=24581;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done, $C. The Scourge military command out of Naxxramas has been thrown into disarray by Razuvious\'s demise.' WHERE entry=24582;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Children everywhere will sleep easier knowing that Patchwerk is no more.' WHERE entry=24583;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='With Malygos defeated, the Nexus War should come to a swift conclusion. You have the gratitude of the Kirin Tor, $N.' WHERE entry=24584;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I never cease to be amazed by the horrors that can be created through the use of technology.' WHERE entry=24585;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Razorscale normally keeps to her aerie near the Colossal Forge in Ulduar. Of late, however, she has been spotted reigning fire down upon lands outside of the titan complex.$B$BThough the broodmother\'s is a sad tale, she poses an imminent threat to all of Northrend. The Council of Six has decreed that Razorscale must die!',offerrewardtext_loc4='Now Veranus can finally rest in peace.' WHERE entry=24586;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I trust that you did not have to face too many of his iron construct assistants?' WHERE entry=24587;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The greatest weakness of Ulduar is its masters\' blind faith in their inventions to protect it.' WHERE entry=24588;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='All of Azeroth is fortunate that Timear foresaw the Eredar lord\'s arrival and that you were there in time to slay him.' WHERE entry=24589;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The Frozen Throne is without its chief guardian thanks to you. Our attacks upon the Lich King\'s forces will be all the more successful now.' WHERE entry=24590;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Sunwell and the end of Quel\'Delar\'s exile await, $N.$B$BYou will find Lor\'themar Theron, the regent of Quel\'Thalas, and Grand Magister Rommath standing within. Be wary of them and do not allow them to entrap you in their political scheming.$B$BInstead, remain focused on your task here. Speak to a Warden of the Sunwell to enter the Sunwell Plateau. Immerse the reformed Quel\'Delar in the Sunwell to complete the restoration. Show the blade to Myralion Sunblaze at Quel\'Delar\'s Rest once it is restored.',objectives_loc4='Immerse your Tainted Quel\'Delar in the Sunwell. Speak to a Warden of the Sunwell when you are ready to enter the Sunwell Plateau.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE entry=24594;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Immerse your Tainted Quel\'Delar in the Sunwell. Speak to a Warden of the Sunwell when you are ready to enter the Sunwell Plateau.$B',objectives_loc4='Immerse your Tainted Quel\'Delar in the Sunwell. Speak to a Warden of the Sunwell when you are ready to enter the Sunwell Plateau.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE entry=24595;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Immerse your Tainted Quel\'Delar in the Sunwell. Speak to a Warden of the Sunwell when you are ready to enter the Sunwell Plateau.$B',objectives_loc4='Immerse your Tainted Quel\'Delar in the Sunwell. Speak to a Warden of the Sunwell when you are ready to enter the Sunwell Plateau.$B' WHERE entry=24596;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to King Varian Wrynn in Stormwind.' WHERE entry=24597;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The Sunwell and the end of Quel\'Delar\'s exile await, $N.$B$BYou will find Lor\'themar Theron, the regent of Quel\'Thalas, and Grand Magister Rommath standing within. Be wary of them and do not allow them to entrap you in their political scheming.$B$BInstead, remain focused on your task here. Immerse the reformed Quel\'Delar in the Sunwell to complete its restoration, then show it to Myralio Sunblaze at Quel\'Delar\'s Rest. Speak to a Warden of the Sunwell when you are ready to enter the Sunwell Plateau.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE entry=24598;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Did you want to make a Lovely Charm Bracelet for the Lord of Ironforge? I\'m sure he\'d be thrilled.$B$BDo you already have a Lovely Charm Collector\'s Kit?',objectives_loc4='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to King Magni Bronzebeard in Ironforge.' WHERE entry=24609;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Did you want to make a Lovely Charm Bracelet for the Warchief? I\'m sure he\'d be thrilled.$B$BDo you already have a Lovely Charm Collector\'s Kit?',objectives_loc4='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to Thrall in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24612;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to Cairne Bloodhoof in Thunder Bluff.' WHERE entry=24614;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Did you want to make a Lovely Charm Bracelet for the Regent Lord of Quel\'Thalas? I\'m sure he\'d be thrilled.$B$BDo you already have a Lovely Charm Collector\'s Kit?',objectives_loc4='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to Lor\'themar Theron in Silvermoon City.' WHERE entry=24615;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Lovely work, $N! People will be tripping over one another to get Crown chocolates now that they\'ve had a chance to taste those sweet, romantic treats.$B$BHere\'s a little something for helping us out.' WHERE entry=24636;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s right outside Orgrimmar\'s gates, to the west! That can\'t be good. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Lackeys and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to damage one Chemical Wagon just west of Orgrimmar\'s gates in Durotar, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24638;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s just outside Ambermill in Silverpine Forest. That can\'t be good. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Thugs and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon outside of Ambermill in Silverpine Forest, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24645;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s just outside the village of Hillsbrad in -- you guessed it -- Hillsbrad Foothills. That can\'t be good. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Dusters and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon just outside of Hillsbrad Village in Hillsbrad Foothills, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24647;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s near Sentry Point, just outside Theramore in Dustwallow. Don\'t give me that look, okay? This is a problem for us, too. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Hoodlums and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon outside of Theramore in Dustwallow Marsh, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24648;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s to the east of Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands. Don\'t give me that look, okay? This is a problem for the Horde, too. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Agents and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon east of Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24649;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s in Winterspring, just east of Everlook. Oh, now this is personal. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Sprinklers and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon east of Everlook in Winterspring, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24650;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it looks like it\'s just east of Shattrath, in Terokkar Forest. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Underlings and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon east of Shattrath City in Terokkar Forest, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24651;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it looks like it\'s in the Forlorn Woods of Crystalsong, northwest of the Mirror of Twilight. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Sprayers and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon in the Forlorn Woods of Crystalsong Forest, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24652;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Get a load of these guys, would ya? Steamwheedle\'s been handling the business of holidays for years, and all of a sudden, these guys bust into the market. They\'re not Steamwheedle; the cartel hired me to get to the bottom of this. Something stinks here and it ain\'t just perfume.$B$BTake this device I brought and go analyze the perfume clouds around the guards. I want to know what they\'re putting in that stuff. Things ain\'t natural.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Hey, thanks, kid. Give it over, let\'s take a look.
<He takes the device from you and fiddles with it.>
Oh, that ain\'t good.' WHERE entry=24655;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='I knew they were up to no good! There\'s some sort of mind-affecting chemical in here, but I can\'t get a handle on it with such a small sample. I need the real stuff.$B$BDon\'t just go over there and buy it! I don\'t want you giving these scumbags one copper. Nah, you gotta get it from the source, discreet-like.$B$BI\'ll disguise you as a package runner. I saw a stockpile guarded by their goons outside the gates. Go run by, and DON\'T stop, or they\'ll make you! They\'ll toss you a crate. Bring it back here.',offerrewardtext_loc4='You got it, huh? Good job, kid. Top notch. Let\'s see what we got here.
<He cracks open the crate and rummages around inside.>' WHERE entry=24656;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You got his ledger? Really? That\'s great, $N. There\'s probably loads of good information in here.' WHERE entry=24657;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s northeast of Westbrook Garrison right outside in Elwynn! That can\'t be good. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Lackeys and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to damage one Chemical Wagon northeast of Westbrook Garrison in Elwynn Forest, then return to Inspector Snip Snagglebolt in Stormwind.' WHERE entry=24658;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s just south of the Grove of the Ancients in Darkshore. That can\'t be good. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Thugs and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon south of the Grove of the Ancients in Darkshore, then return to Inspector Snip Snagglebolt in Stormwind.' WHERE entry=24659;
