UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s in Winterspring, just east of Everlook. Oh, now this is personal. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Sprinklers and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon east of Everlook in Winterspring, then return to Inspector Snip Snagglebolt in Stormwind.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE entry=24664;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it looks like it\'s just east of Shattrath, in Terokkar Forest. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Underlings and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon east of Shattrath City in Terokkar Forest, then return to Inspector Snip Snagglebolt in Stormwind.' WHERE entry=24665;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it looks like it\'s in the Forlorn Woods of Crystalsong, northwest of the Mirror of Twilight. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',objectives_loc4='Kill 5 Crown Sprayers and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon in the Forlorn Woods of Crystalsong Forest, then return to Inspector Snip Snagglebolt in Stormwind.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE entry=24666;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Meet Lady Sylvanas Windrunner inside the entrace to the Pit of Saron.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Incapable fools. I begin to wonder if any of these louts from the tournament will be of any use at all. Perhaps you\'ll prove me wrong.' WHERE entry=24682;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I underestimated this Scourgelord, and it\'s my men that paid for it. When I think that my guilt over Arthas\' betrayal cannot go any deeper, he proves me wrong yet again.$B$BWe have to press on. We cannot let their sacrifice be meaningless.' WHERE entry=24683;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Such a senseless waste! Arthas goes too far! I can only hope what we find in the Halls of Reflection makes this somehow worth it.$B$BIf what that vile gnome said is to be trusted, Frostmourne should be there, and with it, answers to confronting Arthas.' WHERE entry=24710;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='We must press on, hero. We\'ve come so far... we\'re so close to our goal. I must delay a moment to send Elandra back to the airship. I\'m uncertain how we\'re going to escape with so many men lost and so few to keep our path in secure - we will need any help they can send.$B$BContinue on. I will meet you in the Halls of Reflection.',offerrewardtext_loc4='The Halls of Reflection. Finally.$B$BLet me know when you are ready. Arthas may not be here, but it would be naive to think that he would leave Frostmourne unguarded entirely.' WHERE entry=24711;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='The Halls of Reflection lie ahead. If what that vile gnome said is to be trusted, Frostmourne should be there, and with it, answers to confronting Arthas.' WHERE entry=24712;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Keep moving, the sword is close.$B$BI need a moment to send one of my Dark Rangers back to the airship. With all of our fodder gone, I will not be caught unprepared - we will need any help they can send.$B$BGo. I will meet you in the Halls of Reflection.',offerrewardtext_loc4='The Halls of Reflection. Finally.$B$BLet me know when you are ready, $C. I will not be so naive as to think that Arthas left his precious sword entirely unguarded.' WHERE entry=24713;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Listen well, $C. In accepting this weapon your fate is sealed.$B$BOvercome or succumb.$B$BI have placed your feet upon this path. You are therefore my personal responsibility. Should you falter, I am duty-bound to deliver you from this life.$B$BRemember my words, $C, and do not fail.' WHERE entry=24743;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Fantastic. Help is exactly what I need.' WHERE entry=24792;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='That a weapon of such power has been redeemed from the clutches of evil is a great omen in these times, $N. With Quel\'Delar and staunch Silver Covenant allies at our side, the Lich King will have good reason to fear.$B$BThe crusade maintains an arsenal of exceptional weapons for our strongest allies. Allow me to offer you your choice from among them in return for entrusting us with the care of Quel\'Delar.' WHERE entry=24795;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is nothing short of an amazing accomplishment, $N. The day that Thalorien and Anasterian fell, the same day that Quel\'Delar was lost, was one of the darkest of my life. To see Quel\'Delar restored... it is beyond words.$B$BWithout a doubt, you are meant to be the true bearer of the blade. Quel\'Delar\'s magic is already adapting the blade to your skills and your strengths.' WHERE entry=24796;
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc4='A Victory For The Sunreavers',details_loc4='At last, Quel\'Delar is restored for the glory of the Sunreavers and the sin\'dorei!$B$BAll of Silvermoon will celebrate you as a hero, $N.$B$BAs a $C, the sword seems to know you lack the training to wield it and hasn\'t bonded to you. Where, then, will its next master come from? No worthy sin\'dorei has come forward. Let us seek the Argent Crusade\'s counsel. Go north to the Argent Tournament Grounds and present the sword to Justicar Mariel Trueheart on behalf of the Sunreavers.' WHERE entry=24798;
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc4='A Victory For The Sunreavers',details_loc4='At last, Quel\'Delar is restored for the glory of the Sunreavers!$B$BAll the Horde will celebrate you as a hero, $N.$B$BAs a $C, the sword seems to know you lack the training to wield it and hasn\'t bonded to you. Where, then, will its next master come from? I will not conceal my disappointment; I had hoped it would be a worthy sin\'dorei. Let us seek the Argent Crusade\'s counsel. Go north to the Argent Tournament Grounds and present the sword to Justicar Mariel Trueheart on behalf of the Sunreavers.' WHERE entry=24799;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Uther knew a great deal about how Arthas might be defeated. It\'s hard to believe that there is much hope of defeating Arthas upon the steps of his own throne. And who will take up the crown of Lich King if it comes to that?$B$BMany questions remain, but the answers that you\'ve uncovered may be critical to ensuring Arthas\' defeat. You need to find Sylvanas and escape the Lich King while there\'s still time.',objectives_loc4='Find Lady Sylvanas Windrunner and escape the Halls of Reflection',offerrewardtext_loc4='Yet again, vengeance slips through my grasp. It\'s hard to believe how much stronger he\'s gotten.$B$BIt was foolish of you to come for me, but it\'s good to know that there are still some champions of the Horde that aren\'t useless cowards. The information Uther gave us may well be key to finally killing Arthas, though it is becoming more and more clear that the Horde will not be able to accomplish this on their own.$B$BGo, $C. I expect your prowess may be needed again very soon.' WHERE entry=24802;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Don\'t just stand there! Give me the shark and I\'ll declare you the winner!' WHERE entry=24803;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'m afraid we\'ve already had a winner for today, young $N. However, if you bring a shark, I\'ll see that it\'s released back into the waters, and I might just have a little something for you...' WHERE entry=24806;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='To atone for the sins I committed as one of the Lich King\'s Death Knights, I\'ve dedicated myself to creating rings of great power for our brothers and sisters to use in the struggle.$B$BYou\'ve proven yourself as a valuable ally in the fight against the Scourge, $N. As your dedication continues I can improve on the ring\'s original design.$B$BChoose your path carefully. A change of heart will come at a price.' WHERE entry=24815;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Look for Snivel Rustrocket in the Stormwind Counting House, the Auction House, and the Barbershop in Stormwind City.',offerrewardtext_loc4='All he talked about was leaving town with all his money? Then he really has abandoned me, hasn\'t he?$B$BOh, $N, I was such a fool to fall for him, but how could I help myself? He was so irresistible!' WHERE entry=24849;
UPDATE locales_quest SET ObjectiveText1_loc4='Stormwind Counting House searched',ObjectiveText2_loc4='Stormwind Auction House searched' WHERE entry=24849;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Look for Snivel Rustrocket in the Orgrimmar Bank, the Auction House, and the Barbershop in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=24851;
UPDATE locales_quest SET ObjectiveText1_loc4='Orgrimmar Bank searched',ObjectiveText2_loc4='Orgrimmar Auction House searched' WHERE entry=24851;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is quite alarming indeed! But with this information we can call on our brethren from Bloodhoof Village to help thwart the attack. You have saved the lives of many $R, $N.' WHERE entry=24857;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Bring the Sealed Chest to Highlord Darion Mograine in Icecrown Citadel.' WHERE entry=24914;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='The elements are restless, $C.  The earthquakes that plague the land and threaten to collapse Ironforge are not normal.  The Earthen Ring are convinced that we must put the elements to rest before they tear Azeroth apart.  We need your help, $N.$B$BI will give you a bag of Earthen Ring supplies.  In it you will find two items, elemental sapta and a cleansing totem.  Use the sapta to see into the elemental world.  Then use the cleansing totem to subdue the agitated earth spirits.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done $N.  But for every element that is subdued another one takes it\'s place.  The solution we have here is merely a stopgap.  Hopefully my brethren in the Earthen Ring are making more headway.' WHERE entry=25055;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Well done $N.  But for every element that is subdued another one takes it\'s place.  The solution we have here is merely a stopgap.  Hopefully my brethren in the Earthen Ring are making more headway.' WHERE entry=25092;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Why would Twilight\'s Hammer take an interest in these tablets? Brann himself wrote that he hardly knows their significance, although he did mention something about becoming one with the earth. I will need to confer with my fellow Explorer\'s League scholars to decipher these as soon as possible.$B$BThank you, $N. Without your aid, these tablets would\'ve fallen into enemy hands.' WHERE entry=25180;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='I\'m expecting the arrival of a courier traveling from Northrend. He\'s carrying a collection of ancient titan treasures, ones I\'m hoping will shed light on my troubling visions. The shaman should\'ve arrived on one of the recent zeppelin flights and I\'m starting to get worried.$B$BHe was to meet me by the zeppelin tower southwest of Orgrimmar\'s gates, but I don\'t want to miss my audience with the warchief. Would you be willing to look for the courier and see what\'s delaying him?',objectives_loc4='Bring the Tablets of Fire to Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Why would Twilight\'s Hammer take an interest in these tablets? Their contents are a mystery to our most learned scholars and deciphering them will take some time. If Twilight\'s Hammer knows about these relics and desires them, what more are they plotting?$B$BWe are most fortunate that you protected them from capture, $N.' WHERE entry=25181;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='You made it through in one piece? You have more gears then I thought, $N!' WHERE entry=25199;
UPDATE locales_quest SET ObjectiveText3_loc4='Cheer with the Drill Sergeant',ObjectiveText4_loc4='Dance with the Drill Sergeant' WHERE entry=25199;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Fantastic work!$B$BThe data I received shows the radiation levels are fully within safety range of our suits. That is excellent news!' WHERE entry=25212;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Harbingers of doom are nothing new on the streets of Orgrimmar, but I\'m worried about this latest batch. These people are organized and they\'ve attracted a lot of attention in the Drag, where they seem to congregate.$B$BI\'ve thought about rounding them up or otherwise disrupting their activities, but that will just drive them underground. We need to find out more about them. Would you go to the Drag, listen to what these doomsayers are spreading, and gather any literature you can find about their ideas?',objectives_loc4='Listen to a speech given by a Doomsayer in the Drag and obtain copies of the pamphlets "Elemental Fire for the Soul", "What Does \'The End of All Things\' Mean for Me?", and "Finding Security and Comfort in a Doomed World".',offerrewardtext_loc4='<Torek reads over the scrolls you collected.>$B$BWhoever these people are, they really mean to gain a following. It looks like they\'re having quite a bit of success. They can\'t be allowed to incite the citizens of Ogrimmar to panic and hysteria. We must discourage interest in this group and learn as much about it as we can.' WHERE entry=25228;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Our engineers have been working on getting our battle machines ready for our assault on Gnomeregan, but we\'re out of pilots!$B$BWe\'ve developed a device called the Motivate-a-Tron, which prevents distraction from other sources and gives the gnome the courage to enlist.$B$BAfter motivating a few Gnome Citizens, lead them out to Captain Tread Sparknozzle out at Steelgrill\'s Depot, just south of Ironforge.$B$BOh, and be careful. The device is still a little experimental.$B',offerrewardtext_loc4='This is the best group of potential pilots you could find?$B$BOkay, well, I\'ll see what I can do.  I\'ve been known to turn even the biggest pile of gnarled gears into a smooth-runnin\' fightin\' machine and I expect no less with this lot.$B$BWell, I guess it\'s time to work!' WHERE entry=25229;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='<Anton reads over the scrolls you collected.>$B$BWhoever put these leaflets together knows how to get attention and from the state of things in Old Town, there\'s no lack of interest. We must act before they can build a significant following in the city. I fear they\'ll use their influence to spread panic throughout the city, paralyzing us.$B$BWe\'ve got to get inside the organization and learn as much as possible.' WHERE entry=25253;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Oh my.  Their reactions were that different?$B$BNot completely what I was expecting, but I think I have a speech that will do.$B$BJust let me find where I put it...' WHERE entry=25283;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Hey, look at that!  You weren\'t blown to bits!' WHERE entry=25285;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Toby is all done with the speech?  Let me see...$B$B<Reads the speech> Pumping pistons! What a fantastic speech! I knew Toby was a good writer, but this is perhaps the best he\'s ever written.$B$BI think it\'s time to get you out to the battle.' WHERE entry=25286;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is the final draft, then?  Let me have a look...' WHERE entry=25287;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc4='Test the the Scuttling Mechano-Tank\'s maneuverability.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Hmm... so the left leg servo was activating the right leg?  But I saw the left leg moving...$B$BEh, details.  I\'ll get to that later, but two out of three things worked: That isn\'t half bad!$B$BThanks for checking this out for me, $N.' WHERE entry=25289;
UPDATE locales_quest SET ObjectiveText3_loc4='Speak to Cultist Tokka',ObjectiveText4_loc4='Speak to Cultist Rokaga' WHERE entry=25293;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Hmm... so the bullets had quite a bit of spread?$B$BTo some people that may be a problem... me, though, I see it as a blessing in disguise!$B$BOur enemies will be running all over the place, so with a bit of a spread, the tank drivers won\'t need to lead the target!' WHERE entry=25295;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='[ph] War!',objectives_loc4='[ph] Log Description' WHERE entry=25306;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Curses! We had to fall back. But Thermaplugg\'s lost, and he knows it... he\'s only bought himself time. We hold the surface, and when the radiation clears we\'ll assault and recapture Gnomeregan with a force twice this size.' WHERE entry=25393;
UPDATE locales_quest SET ObjectiveText3_loc4='Speak to Cultist Wyman',ObjectiveText4_loc4='Speak to Cultist Orlunn' WHERE entry=25414;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='De time for battle is now!  We\'d be headin\' ova to da islands soon, so you\'d betta be ready.$B$BZalazane doesn\'t have much time left.',objectives_loc4='Help Vol\'jin take back the Echo Isles and kill Zalazane.',offerrewardtext_loc4='$N, you\'d be a mighty warrior and a fierce commrade to da Darkspear trolls.  De Echo Isles are OURS now and we couldn\'ta done it wit\'out ya.$B$BTake dis cloak. Wear it wit pride.  You\'d be a member of da tribe now!$B$BIn no time, da trolls will have a home again and we have you to thank for dat.' WHERE entry=25445;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='This is the speech from Toby?  Fantastic!$B$BRecruit, you\'ve done all we could possibly ask for and the Gnomeregan Army thanks you!$B$BWe\'ve got a strike team heading to Gnomeregan now and that wouldn\'t have been possible without your assistance.  For all of your help, we\'d like you to join the Gnomeregan Reserves!$B$BIt doesn\'t pay very well, but you do get this snazzy helmet.  Hang on to that, you might need it someday!' WHERE entry=25500;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='This Elemental Shard is all that is left from the rift that stood here before.  The connection between the shard and the rift is unknown, but perhaps someone more versed in the elements would know more.$B$BSeek out an Earthen Ring Emissary in any capital city.  This could be exactly what they are looking for.',objectives_loc4='Take the Elemental Shard to an Earthen Ring Emissary in Orgrimmar, Undercity, Thunder Bluff or Silvermoon.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Yes, $N, this shard does explain the occurrence of the rifts.  The elemental planes have been in chaos in Outland ever since Draenor was destroyed. These shards cause a weakness in the already damaged elemental planes and allow the elementals to cross over. We\'re still collecting information on who or what is behind all of this.  However, the more shards you bring me, the better prepared we will be to fight the elemental invasion here in Azeroth.' WHERE entry=25571;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Yes, $N, this shard does explain the occurrence of the rift.  The elemental planes have been in chaos in Outland ever since Draenor was destroyed. These shards cause a weakness in the already damaged elemental planes and allow the elementals to cross into our world We\'re still looking into how these rifts are appearing in Azeroth.  Keep bringing us the shards.  Every shard we get brings us closer to understanding how these rifts are appearing.' WHERE entry=25773;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='$R, something terrible has transpired within the Ruby Sanctum beneath the Temple.$B$BThe entry to the Sanctum is in ruins, and its guardians violently slain. We sent scouts to investigate, but they have not returned. I cannot help but fear the worst.$B$BEnter the Ruby Sanctum and discover what has befallen the home of my flight. Once we have more information, we can plan our next steps accordingly.' WHERE entry=26013;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Sandfury trolls and the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer, you say? And they meant to send some giant monster into the heart of the city?! Well done! Stormwind is in your debt.' WHERE entry=26054;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='It appears that the Sandfury trolls are working with the Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BNo matter. That foul witch won\'t be sending her monster to MY city.$B$BCome, brave ones! We\'ll slick the sand with their gore and return home triumphant. Tell Hamuul Runetotem what\'s happened here when we\'ve gotten back; I\'ll need to oversee the return of the citizenry, repairs, and so on.',objectives_loc4='Slay Kai\'ju Gahz\'rilla and inform Hamuul Runetotem in Thunder Bluff.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Sandfury trolls and the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer, you say? And they meant to send some giant monster into the heart of the city?! Well done! Thunder Bluff is in your debt.' WHERE entry=26990;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, ye say? At the behest of the Cult o\' Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Ironforge is in yer debt.' WHERE entry=27122;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Dark Irons? Cho\'gall?! We\'ll show them what becomes of those who attack Orgrimmar.$B$BLet us attack! We\'ll hurl their limbless corpses into the magma they so adore.$B$BYou\'ll tell Blood Guard Kang what\'s happened here when we\'re done, yes? Doubtless I\'ll need to spend time organizing the repair of the city...',objectives_loc4='Slay Grand Ambassador Flamelash and inform Blood Guard Kang in Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, you say? At the behest of the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Orgrimmar is in your debt.' WHERE entry=27127;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='A massive prince of the wind, you say? The herald of Al\'Akir, the Windlord? Madness. All of it. Stormwind is in your debt, hero.' WHERE entry=27207;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='So. This is what evil lies behind the attacks on fair Thunder Bluff.$B$BLet us move forward. It is time to put an end to this abomination.$B$BTell Hamuul Runetotem what has happened here upon our return; I\'ll need to oversee the return of my people, repairs, and the like.',objectives_loc4='Slay Prince Sarsarun and inform Hamuul Runetotem in Thunder Bluff.',offerrewardtext_loc4='A massive prince of the wind, you say? The herald of Al\'Akir, the Windlord? Madness. All of it. All of Thunder Bluff is in your debt, $C.' WHERE entry=27209;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $C.  These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get.' WHERE entry=27307;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc4='Do you feel it, $C?  The elements are uneasy. We members of the Earthen Ring have struggled to find the cause of the unrest.  Thus far we have been unsuccessful and now turn to others that may aid us.  Speak with Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar and see what tasks she may have for you.',objectives_loc4='Speak to Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc4='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $C.  These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get.' WHERE entry=27308;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='It is good that you\'ve come, $N.  We need all the help we can get with the situation here.' WHERE entry=27473;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='Well met, $C.  I am Gavan Grayfeather, emissary of the Wildhammer shaman. There is much work to be done.  The leaders fear for their citizens, as many have turned to cults.  We shaman are concerned with the elemental unrest. Our advice to you, $C, is to be vigilant.  Help where you can, be it calming the people or putting the elementals at rest.  There is plenty to do.' WHERE entry=27540;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='King\'s honor, $C.  I am Captain Anton.  I am leading the investigation into the cultists that have appeared in Stormwind.' WHERE entry=27546;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='It is good to see you, $N.  Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth.' WHERE entry=27566;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc4='It is good to see you, $C.  Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth.' WHERE entry=27572;

SET NAMES 'latin1';
